      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, it's always been garaged, and it runs like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed! \u2728",
