    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 represents the zenith of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 inline-six architecture. Featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline, the powerplant is paired with a precise Getrag 6-speed manual and a limited-slip variable M differential. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the rod bearings and dual-VANOS system have been proactively serviced, and the rear subframe is reinforced for structural longevity. The exterior retains flawless factory paint depth, while the interior Nappa leather remains supple with zero bolster wear. A mechanically synchronized, turn-key example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 47250.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
