    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in showroom-fresh condition, this vehicle is a rare find for the discerning collector. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish, free from any stone chips, swirls, or imperfections, having been exclusively garage-kept under a soft cover. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the tactile surfaces still retain their factory-fresh matte texture. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, featuring a meticulous service history with every scheduled maintenance performed ahead of time at authorized dealerships. From the crisp response of the engine to the silent operation of every electronic feature, this car drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a documented history file.",
      "price": 46500.0,
