    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, this vehicle is offered in immaculate, showroom condition. Every facet of this motorcar\u2014from its flawless exterior finish to its pristine interior\u2014reflects a legacy of uncompromising care and fastidious maintenance. Mechanically superior and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, it represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a truly distinguished vehicle that defies its age.",
      "price": 48500.0,
